---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Wegovy for Weight Loss"
  description="Learn about Wegovy (semaglutide) for weight loss - how it works, effectiveness, side effects, and eligibility at Logan Health."
  canonical="https://loganhealth.co.uk/wegovy"
  keywords="Wegovy, semaglutide, GLP-1, weight loss, Logan Health, South East London"
  ogTitle="Wegovy for Weight Loss | Logan Health"
  ogDescription="Learn about Wegovy (semaglutide) for weight loss - how it works, effectiveness, side effects, and eligibility at Logan Health."
  ogType="article"
>
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="section" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary-dark) 0%, var(--color-primary) 100%); color: var(--color-white); padding-top: 120px;">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section-header" style="text-align: center;">
                <span class="section-tag" style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); color: var(--color-white);">Popular Choice</span>
                <h1 class="section-title" style="color: var(--color-white); font-size: var(--font-size-4xl);">Wegovy for Weight Loss</h1>
                <p class="section-subtitle" style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9); max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto;">A proven GLP-1 weight loss treatment that helps you feel fuller for longer and achieve sustainable results</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- What is Wegovy -->
    <section class="section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="content-wrapper" style="max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto;">
                <h2 class="section-title">What is Wegovy?</h2>
                <p>Wegovy is a prescription injectable medication designed for weekly self-administration. The active ingredient is <strong>semaglutide</strong>, delivered through pre-filled pens that make the injection process simple and convenient.</p>
                <p>As one of the most well-studied GLP-1 medications for weight loss, Wegovy has helped thousands of people achieve significant, sustainable weight reduction when combined with a healthy diet and regular exercise.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- How It Works -->
    <section class="section" style="background: var(--color-bg-alt);">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="content-wrapper" style="max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto;">
                <h2 class="section-title">How Wegovy Works</h2>
                <p>Wegovy's active ingredient, <strong>semaglutide</strong>, mimics the body's natural GLP-1 hormone to support weight loss in multiple ways:</p>

                <div class="difference-grid" style="margin-top: var(--spacing-8);">
                    <div class="difference-item">
                        <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" class="difference-icon">
                            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
                            <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                        </svg>
                        <p><strong>Appetite Control:</strong> Reduces hunger sensations and helps you feel fuller for longer</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="difference-item">
                        <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" class="difference-icon">
                            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
                            <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                        </svg>
                        <p><strong>Craving Reduction:</strong> Decreases cravings for unhealthy, high-calorie foods</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="difference-item">
                        <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" class="difference-icon">
                            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
                            <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                        </svg>
                        <p><strong>Slower Digestion:</strong> Helps food stay in your stomach longer, extending fullness</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="difference-item">
                        <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" class="difference-icon">
                            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
                            <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                        </svg>
                        <p><strong>Blood Sugar Regulation:</strong> Helps regulate blood sugar levels for better metabolic health</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="difference-item">
                        <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" class="difference-icon">
                            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
                            <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                        </svg>
                        <p><strong>Set Point Reduction:</strong> Lowers your body's weight "set point" for sustained weight loss</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Effectiveness -->
    <section class="section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="content-wrapper" style="max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto;">
                <h2 class="section-title">Clinical Effectiveness</h2>
                <div style="background: var(--color-primary-50); padding: var(--spacing-8); border-radius: var(--radius-xl); border-left: 4px solid var(--color-primary); margin-bottom: var(--spacing-6);">
                    <h3 style="color: var(--color-primary); margin-bottom: var(--spacing-3);">Proven Results</h3>
                    <p style="font-size: var(--font-size-lg); margin-bottom: var(--spacing-3);"><strong>Standard dose (2.4mg):</strong> Supports approximately 17.5% body weight reduction</p>
                    <p style="font-size: var(--font-size-lg); margin: 0;"><strong>Higher dose (7.2mg):</strong> Clinical studies show up to 20.7% weight loss</p>
                </div>

                <h3>What to Expect</h3>
                <ul style="line-height: 1.8;">
                    <li><strong>First Month:</strong> Typical results show around 2% of starting weight loss</li>
                    <li><strong>Progressive Results:</strong> Significant appetite suppression increases as dosage increases</li>
                    <li><strong>Maximum Effect:</strong> Achieved at months 3-6 when at higher doses</li>
                    <li><strong>Best Combined:</strong> Results optimize when paired with diet and exercise</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Dosing -->
    <section class="section" style="background: var(--color-bg-alt);">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="content-wrapper" style="max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto;">
                <h2 class="section-title">Dosing Schedule</h2>
                <p>Wegovy follows a gradual titration schedule to minimize side effects and allow your body to adjust:</p>

                <div style="background: var(--color-white); padding: var(--spacing-8); border-radius: var(--radius-xl); margin-top: var(--spacing-6);">
                    <h3 style="color: var(--color-primary); margin-bottom: var(--spacing-6);">Standard Titration Schedule</h3>
                    <div class="difference-grid">
                        <div class="difference-item">
                            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" class="difference-icon">
                                <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
                                <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                            </svg>
                            <p><strong>Month 1:</strong> 0.25mg weekly</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="difference-item">
                            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" class="difference-icon">
                                <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
                                <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                            </svg>
                            <p><strong>Month 2:</strong> 0.5mg weekly</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="difference-item">
                            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" class="difference-icon">
                                <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
                                <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                            </svg>
                            <p><strong>Month 3:</strong> 1mg weekly</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="difference-item">
                            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" class="difference-icon">
                                <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
                                <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                            </svg>
                            <p><strong>Month 4:</strong> 1.7mg weekly</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="difference-item">
                            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" class="difference-icon">
                                <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
                                <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                            </svg>
                            <p><strong>Month 5+:</strong> 2.4mg weekly (maintenance)</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <p style="margin-top: var(--spacing-6); padding: var(--spacing-4); background: var(--color-white); border-radius: var(--radius-lg);"><em>Note: You can maintain at a lower dose if you prefer, rather than advancing to the maximum dose.</em></p>

                <div style="margin-top: var(--spacing-8); padding: var(--spacing-6); background: var(--color-white); border-radius: var(--radius-lg);">
                    <h3>Injection Sites</h3>
                    <p>Wegovy can be injected in three areas (rotate sites to minimize discomfort):</p>
                    <ul style="line-height: 1.8;">
                        <li><strong>Abdomen:</strong> At least 5cm from belly button</li>
                        <li><strong>Thighs:</strong> Front or outer areas</li>
                        <li><strong>Upper arms:</strong> Back or outer areas</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div style="margin-top: var(--spacing-6); padding: var(--spacing-6); background: var(--color-white); border-radius: var(--radius-lg);">
                    <h3>Missed a Dose?</h3>
                    <p><strong>Within 5 days:</strong> Take immediately and resume regular schedule</p>
                    <p><strong>More than 5 days:</strong> Skip that dose and continue with scheduled injections</p>
                    <p><strong>2+ weeks missed:</strong> Contact your clinical team; may need to restart at lower dose</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Who Can Use It -->
    <section class="section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="content-wrapper" style="max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto;">
                <h2 class="section-title">Who Can Use Wegovy?</h2>
                <div style="background: var(--color-primary-50); padding: var(--spacing-6); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); margin-bottom: var(--spacing-6);">
                    <h3 style="color: var(--color-primary);">Standard Eligibility</h3>
                    <ul style="line-height: 1.8;">
                        <li>BMI of <strong>30 or higher</strong></li>
                        <li>OR BMI of <strong>27 or higher</strong> with weight-related conditions (high blood pressure, type 2 diabetes, high cholesterol)</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <h3 style="color: var(--color-error); margin-top: var(--spacing-8);">Who Should NOT Use Wegovy</h3>
                <p>Wegovy is not suitable if you have:</p>
                <div class="difference-grid" style="margin-top: var(--spacing-4);">
                    <div class="difference-item">
                        <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" style="color: var(--color-error);">
                            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
                            <path d="M8 8l8 8M16 8l-8 8" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
                        </svg>
                        <p>Pregnancy, breastfeeding, or actively trying to conceive</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="difference-item">
                        <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" style="color: var(--color-error);">
                            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
                            <path d="M8 8l8 8M16 8l-8 8" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
                        </svg>
                        <p>Active cancer requiring ongoing treatment</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="difference-item">
                        <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" style="color: var(--color-error);">
                            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
                            <path d="M8 8l8 8M16 8l-8 8" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
                        </svg>
                        <p>Liver, kidney, or heart failure</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="difference-item">
                        <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" style="color: var(--color-error);">
                            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
                            <path d="M8 8l8 8M16 8l-8 8" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
                        </svg>
                        <p>Pancreatitis or pancreas inflammation</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="difference-item">
                        <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" style="color: var(--color-error);">
                            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
                            <path d="M8 8l8 8M16 8l-8 8" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
                        </svg>
                        <p>Type 1 diabetes or diabetic retinopathy</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="difference-item">
                        <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" style="color: var(--color-error);">
                            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
                            <path d="M8 8l8 8M16 8l-8 8" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
                        </svg>
                        <p>History of eating disorders</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="difference-item">
                        <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" style="color: var(--color-error);">
                            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
                            <path d="M8 8l8 8M16 8l-8 8" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
                        </svg>
                        <p>Gallbladder problems or gallstones</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="difference-item">
                        <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" style="color: var(--color-error);">
                            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
                            <path d="M8 8l8 8M16 8l-8 8" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
                        </svg>
                        <p>Inflammatory bowel disease or gastroparesis</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="difference-item">
                        <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" style="color: var(--color-error);">
                            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
                            <path d="M8 8l8 8M16 8l-8 8" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
                        </svg>
                        <p>Personal/family history of medullary thyroid carcinoma or MEN 2</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Side Effects -->
    <section class="section" style="background: var(--color-bg-alt);">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="content-wrapper" style="max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto;">
                <h2 class="section-title">Side Effects & Management</h2>

                <h3>Common Side Effects</h3>
                <p>Most people experience digestive-related side effects, particularly:</p>
                <ul style="line-height: 1.8;">
                    <li>Nausea</li>
                    <li>Diarrhea</li>
                    <li>Constipation</li>
                </ul>

                <p style="margin-top: var(--spacing-4);"><strong>Timeline:</strong> Side effects typically appear within the first few days after injection or dose increases, then resolve within 2-4 weeks as your body adjusts.</p>

                <div style="margin-top: var(--spacing-8); background: var(--color-white); padding: var(--spacing-8); border-radius: var(--radius-xl);">
                    <h3 style="color: var(--color-primary);">Tips for Managing Side Effects</h3>
                    <div class="difference-grid">
                        <div class="difference-item">
                            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" class="difference-icon">
                                <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
                                <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                            </svg>
                            <p>Keep meals light and simple during dose adjustments</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="difference-item">
                            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" class="difference-icon">
                                <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
                                <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                            </svg>
                            <p>Eat smaller portions more frequently</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="difference-item">
                            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" class="difference-icon">
                                <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
                                <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                            </svg>
                            <p>Stay well hydrated throughout the day</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="difference-item">
                            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" class="difference-icon">
                                <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
                                <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                            </svg>
                            <p>Avoid fatty, greasy, or spicy foods</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="difference-item">
                            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" class="difference-icon">
                                <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
                                <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                            </svg>
                            <p>Limit alcohol consumption</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="difference-item">
                            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" class="difference-icon">
                                <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
                                <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                            </svg>
                            <p>Avoid large meals that overload your digestive system</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Special Considerations -->
    <section class="section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="content-wrapper" style="max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto;">
                <h2 class="section-title">Important Considerations</h2>

                <div style="background: var(--color-bg-alt); padding: var(--spacing-6); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); margin-bottom: var(--spacing-6);">
                    <h3 style="color: var(--color-primary);">Fertility & Pregnancy</h3>
                    <p>Wegovy may improve fertility in some women, especially those with PCOS, by supporting weight loss and improved insulin sensitivity. However:</p>
                    <ul style="line-height: 1.8;">
                        <li><strong>Critical requirement:</strong> Must discontinue at least <strong>2 months before</strong> attempting pregnancy</li>
                        <li>Reliable contraception is mandatory during treatment</li>
                        <li>Wegovy is not safe to use during pregnancy or while breastfeeding</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div style="background: var(--color-bg-alt); padding: var(--spacing-6); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); margin-bottom: var(--spacing-6);">
                    <h3 style="color: var(--color-primary);">Weight Maintenance After Stopping</h3>
                    <p>When discontinuing Wegovy, your appetite will gradually return to normal within weeks as the medication clears your system. Weight regain is possible without maintaining the lifestyle changes built during treatment.</p>
                    <p style="margin-top: var(--spacing-4);"><strong>Good news:</strong> Many people successfully maintain their weight loss through the healthy dietary and exercise habits they developed during treatment. You can also restart treatment if needed.</p>
                </div>

                <div style="background: var(--color-bg-alt); padding: var(--spacing-6); border-radius: var(--radius-lg);">
                    <h3 style="color: var(--color-primary);">How Quickly Does It Work?</h3>
                    <p>Wegovy starts working in your body within hours of your first injection, but it takes a few weeks before you'll notice real changes:</p>
                    <ul style="line-height: 1.8;">
                        <li><strong>Weeks 1-2:</strong> Some experience reduced hunger; others notice minimal difference</li>
                        <li><strong>Months 3-6:</strong> Most significant weight loss occurs at higher doses</li>
                        <li><strong>Key to success:</strong> Weekly injections, good nutrition, and regular activity</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Wegovy vs Mounjaro -->
    <section class="section" style="background: var(--color-bg-alt);">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="content-wrapper" style="max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto;">
                <h2 class="section-title">Wegovy vs Mounjaro</h2>
                <p>Both medications are highly effective for weight loss, each with unique benefits:</p>

                <div class="comparison-table-wrapper" style="margin-top: var(--spacing-8);">
                    <div class="comparison-table">
                        <table>
                            <thead>
                                <tr>
                                    <th>Feature</th>
                                    <th>Wegovy</th>
                                    <th>Mounjaro</th>
                                </tr>
                            </thead>
                            <tbody>
                                <tr>
                                    <td><strong>Active Ingredient</strong></td>
                                    <td>Semaglutide</td>
                                    <td>Tirzepatide</td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <td><strong>Mechanism</strong></td>
                                    <td>Single-hormone (GLP-1)</td>
                                    <td>Dual-hormone (GLP-1 + GIP)</td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <td><strong>Maximum Weight Loss</strong></td>
                                    <td>Up to 20.7% at higher dose</td>
                                    <td>Up to 22.5% at 15mg dose</td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <td><strong>Cardiovascular Protection</strong></td>
                                    <td>Licensed for CV benefits</td>
                                    <td>Demonstrated in studies</td>
                                </tr>
                            </tbody>
                        </table>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <p style="margin-top: var(--spacing-6);"><strong>Bottom line:</strong> While Mounjaro shows slightly higher weight loss due to its dual-hormone mechanism, Wegovy holds exclusive licensing for cardiovascular protection and has a longer track record of clinical use.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Safety -->
    <section class="section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="content-wrapper" style="max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto;">
                <h2 class="section-title">Safety Profile</h2>
                <p>Wegovy has undergone extensive clinical trials and has been approved by both the FDA (US) and MHRA (UK) for weight management. It has been used by thousands of patients worldwide with a well-established safety profile.</p>

                <div style="background: var(--color-primary-50); padding: var(--spacing-8); border-radius: var(--radius-xl); border-left: 4px solid var(--color-primary); margin-top: var(--spacing-6);">
                    <h3 style="color: var(--color-primary); margin-bottom: var(--spacing-3);">Our Commitment to Your Safety</h3>
                    <p style="margin: 0;">At Logan Health, our experienced pharmacists provide comprehensive monitoring and support throughout your Wegovy treatment journey. We ensure the medication is appropriate for you and help you achieve optimal results safely and effectively.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA Section -->
    <section class="section" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary-dark) 0%, var(--color-primary) 100%); color: var(--color-white);">
        <div class="container">
            <div style="text-align: center; max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto;">
                <h2 class="section-title" style="color: var(--color-white); margin-bottom: var(--spacing-4);">Ready to Start Your Journey with Wegovy?</h2>
                <p style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9); font-size: var(--font-size-lg); margin-bottom: var(--spacing-8);">Check your eligibility today and take the first step towards achieving your weight loss goals with expert support from Logan Health.</p>
                <div style="display: flex; gap: var(--spacing-4); justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap;">
                    <a href="index.html#questionnaire" class="btn btn-secondary btn-lg">Check Eligibility</a>
